{
  "name": "SMB AI 13 — Multi-Source Knowledge Sync",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Live deployment checklist\n\nWorkflow: SMB AI 13 — Multi-Source Knowledge Sync\nNodes: 13\nTrigger: Daily 6pm, Hourly Ingest\nCredentials/services: Gmail OAuth, Meeting transcript provider, Notion, OpenAI, OpenAI embeddings, Qdrant, Slack OAuth\nPlaceholders: #knowledge, YOUR_KNOWLEDGE_DB\nEnvironment variables: None detected\nExternal webhook setup: not required\n\nBefore activating:\n1. Configure every credential in n8n Credentials.\n2. Replace every placeholder above with live IDs, channels, folders, or database IDs.\n3. Execute once with test data and inspect every node output.\n4. Activate only after the workflow reaches its final node successfully.",
        "height": 440,
        "width": 520,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "live-2896f467f4916a29788940c2",
      "name": "Live Deployment Checklist",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        80,
        -140
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "hours",
              "hoursInterval": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      },
